The SynHighlighterASM unit provides SynEdit with a x86 Assembler (.asm) highlighter.
The highlighter supports all x86 op codes, Intel MMX and AMD 3D NOW! op codes.
Thanks to Martin Waldenburg, Hideo Koiso.
